		<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Paladins & Bows</b></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><A href="mailto:KKPartin@email.msn.com">Ahmen</a> | 
		            5/31/1999 6:58:23 PM</b></font></p>
		         <a href="guides.asp">
		         <font face="verdana" size="2">Return to guide listing.</font></a>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">There seems to be some question of whether a Paladin can use a bow.  I am a level 20 Paladin (not ranger) and I can use a bow just fine.  Archery is even a choice for me to train at the Paladin trainer.  I first noticed this when I was around level 17.  I dont know if it was something that was changed with a patch or whether it is a level thing.  I do know that earlier I was not able to use a bow but I can now.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
				<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>
